Don't make all of them look selected on down arrow
When it has focus and you press down arrow, it says how many are in the list
When it has focus and you type a character, it opens the box and sets focus in the field and selects the first item, and says how many are in the list
When it is open and you press Enter, it selects the option in the select and adds checkmark
You can arrow up and down
You can click on an option
It sends the data to the <select multiple>
The style looks like the original
It has a button like the original


